# The image build context is the repo root (ops/compose.yml) only so the
# reporting crate's include_bytes!(".../docs/reference/*.xlsx") golden templates
# are reachable at compile time. Everything else must be excluded — notably
# .claude/worktrees (hundreds of GB) and backend/target (tens of GB) — or the
# context transfer is catastrophic.
#
# Strategy: ignore everything, then re-include only the build inputs.
*

!backend
!docs

# Prune heavy / irrelevant paths back out of the re-included trees.
backend/target
backend/.sqlx/query-*.tmp
docs/evidence
**/.DS_Store
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/node_modules
**/.git
